/* ProfileSettingsView — Network Isolation */
"Restrict which networks and ports this browser can reach" = "Restreignez les r\U00E9seaux et les ports accessibles par ce navigateur";
"Isolate from Local Network" = "Isoler du r\U00E9seau local";
"Prevents this browser from reaching devices on your home or office network, like printers, NAS drives, or internal servers. Internet access is not affected." = "Emp\U00EAche ce navigateur d\U2019atteindre les appareils de votre r\U00E9seau domestique ou professionnel, tels que les imprimantes, les NAS ou les serveurs internes. L\U2019acc\U00E8s \U00E0 Internet n\U2019est pas affect\U00E9.";
"Restrict Outgoing Ports" = "Restreindre les ports sortants";
"Only allow the browser to connect on specific network ports. Useful for locking down which services the browser can reach." = "N\U2019autorise le navigateur \U00E0 se connecter que sur des ports r\U00E9seau sp\U00E9cifiques. Utile pour limiter les services accessibles par le navigateur.";
"Allowed ports (e.g. 80, 443, 8000-9000)" = "Ports autoris\U00E9s (p. ex. 80, 443, 8000-9000)";
"DNS (port 53) is always allowed. Separate ports with commas. Use a dash for ranges." = "Le DNS (port 53) est toujours autoris\U00E9. S\U00E9parez les ports par des virgules. Utilisez un tiret pour les plages.";

