"WireGuard" = "WireGuard";
"Choose a VPN to route browser traffic through an encrypted tunnel, hiding your IP address from websites." = "Choisissez un VPN pour acheminer le trafic du navigateur \U00E0 travers un tunnel chiffr\U00E9, masquant votre adresse IP aux sites web.";
