/* ProfileSettingsView — Session Recording */
"Session Recording" = "Enregistrement de session";
"Record all HTTP requests made during this browsing session. Useful for analyzing what a suspicious link does behind the scenes. When the session ends, you can save or discard the recording." = "Enregistre toutes les requ\U00EAtes HTTP effectu\U00E9es pendant cette session de navigation. Utile pour analyser ce qu\U2019un lien suspect fait en arri\U00E8re-plan. \U00C0 la fin de la session, vous pouvez sauvegarder ou supprimer l\U2019enregistrement.";
"Capture Level" = "Niveau de capture";
"Disabled" = "D\U00E9sactiv\U00E9";
"Basic \U2014 URLs only" = "Basique \U2014 URL uniquement";
"Headers \U2014 URLs + headers + POST data" = "En-t\U00EAtes \U2014 URL + en-t\U00EAtes + donn\U00E9es POST";
"Full \U2014 URLs + headers + response bodies" = "Complet \U2014 URL + en-t\U00EAtes + corps des r\U00E9ponses";
"This level captures POST data which may include passwords, tokens, and form submissions in clear text." = "Ce niveau capture les donn\U00E9es POST, qui peuvent inclure des mots de passe, des jetons et des soumissions de formulaires en clair.";
"Full capture records all request and response bodies including passwords, authentication tokens, personal data, and any sensitive content transmitted over the network. Use only for security analysis of untrusted links." = "La capture compl\U00E8te enregistre tous les corps de requ\U00EAtes et de r\U00E9ponses, y compris les mots de passe, les jetons d\U2019authentification, les donn\U00E9es personnelles et tout contenu sensible transmis sur le r\U00E9seau. \U00C0 utiliser uniquement pour l\U2019analyse de s\U00E9curit\U00E9 de liens non fiables.";

